item.title: ONYON + Cesar Palace + Kevin Diesel + Doc Flippers
item.description: This Sunday, March 26th @ Hitness Club we are hosting a MATINÉE (!!) Show: Doors 16h00 // First band (⪧ ͟ل͜⪦)━☆ﾟ.*･｡ﾟ 17h00 (écharpe!) // bands should be done by 21h00 !! Poster eggplant by Aranzazu Morena ONYON [wavy punk] This local quartet volleys hits and hits and hits on end! So, get a good dose of ant-like rhythms, whippy guitars, with an icing of synthscapes and some bel cantos on top.
